If i'm honest, then my approach would've been to force this downgrade if freqai-rl (or dev) is selected (we do something similar with cython for raspberry installations).

It's not really optional - and we know for a fact that installation will fail if this requirement is not matched - so we're basically asking the user "would you like to have the installation fail - or not?" - without saying it out loud 😆 

It's not a global downgrade anyway, and will only impact the current virtual environment - so it's not problematic i'd think.



